Package: EffToxDesign
Type: Package
Title: Dose-Finding Clinical Trial Design Based on Efficacy-Toxicity Trade-Offs
Version: 0.1
Date: 2018-05-05
Authors@R: c(person("Brian J", "Smith", email = "brian-j-smith@uiowa.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Kristian", "Brock", email = "kristian.brock@gmail.com", role = c("aut")),
             person("Brian J", "Smith", role = "cph"))
Maintainer: Brian J Smith <brian-j-smith@uiowa.edu>
Description: An adaptive Bayesian method for dose-finding in phase I/II clinical trials based on trade-offs between the probabilities of treatment efficacy and toxicity, as developed by Thall and Cood (2004, Biometrics 60, 684-693).
License: GPL-3
